# ğŸŒ¾ Krishi Samadhan - Multilingual Agri-Advisor Chatbot

**Krishi Samadhan** is a sophisticated, web-based AI chatbot designed to serve as a comprehensive agricultural advisor.  
Built with **Vanilla JavaScript**, it integrates powerful AI and speech services to provide **multilingual support**, **location-aware advice**, and **context-based answers** from user-uploaded documents.

